import { FormControl, FormLabel, Input, VStack } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import React from 'react'

const Signup = () => {
  return (
    <VStack spacing={'5px'}>
          <FormControl>
              <FormLabel>
                  <Input>
                      placeholder="Name"
                      onChange
                  </Input>
              </FormLabel>
      </FormControl>
    </VStack>
  )
}

export default Signup
